2013年，事务所被描述成共同代表在巴拿马注册的超过半数公司的七家公司之一<ref>{{cite news |url=http://laestrella.com.pa/online/impreso/2013/03/08/acciones-al-portador-provocan-divisiones.asp |title=Acciones al portador provocan divisiones |author=Alma Solís |accessdate=March 8, 2013 |date=March 8, 2013 |publisher=''[[La_Estrella_de_Panamá|La Estrella de Panamá]]'' |language=es |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130313054928/http://www.laestrella.com.pa/online/impreso/2013/03/08/acciones-al-portador-provocan-divisiones.asp |archivedate=2013-03-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。事务所在其各办事处中还拥有多个在巴拿马注册的公司<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.elconfidencial.com/espana/2013-02-15/gonzalez-pasa-al-ataque-contra-el-sup-por-las-acusaciones-sobre-su-atico_228723/ |title=González pasa al ataque contra el SUP por las acusaciones sobre su ático |author=José María Olmo |accessdate=March 8, 2013 |date=February 15, 2013 |publisher=''[[El_Confidencial|El Confidencial]]''}}</ref>。它是企业服务行业内最大的事务所之一<ref name=econ>{{cite news |url=http://www.economist.com/node/21552196 |title=Shells and shelves |publisher=''[[The_Economist|The Economist]]'' |accessdate=March 8, 2013 |date=April 7, 2012 |archive-date=2013-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130314174145/http://www.economist.com/node/21552196 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 但创始人声称，该事务所只占全球金融服务法律行业的5％左右<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/ec5952e0-fad6-11e5-8f41-df5bda8beb40.html#axzz44xjbGZwu|title=Mossack Fonseca founder dismisses Panama Papers as ‘witch hunt’|last=Webber|first=Jude|date=2016-04-05|newspaper=Financial Times|issn=0307-1766|access-date=2016-04-05}}</ref>。

事务所被《[[经济学人|经济学人]]》报形容为“守口如瓶”<ref name="econ" />。

== 办事处与国际业务 ==
该事务所在[[中华人民共和国|中国]]设有九个办事处<ref name="econ" />，[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]有多个<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.miamiherald.com/news/local/community/miami-dade/article69249277.html|title=Panama Papers: Secret offshores trace back to Brickell condo featured on ‘Miami Vice’|website=miamiherald|access-date=2016-04-05}}</ref>，其他位于[[美国|美国]]和[[欧洲|欧洲]]<ref name="AboutMFGroup" />，其中有两个在[[瑞士|瑞士]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.handelszeitung.ch/unternehmen/o-wie-schoen-ist-panama-fuer-steuerfluechtlinge |title=O wie schön ist Panama – für Steuerflüchtlinge |date=February 24, 2010 |accessdate=March 8, 2013 |author=Samuel Gerber |publisher=''{{link-de|Handelszeitung|Handelszeitung}}''}}</ref>。事务所的律师被派往国外推广巴拿马和巴拿马的金融产品<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.iomtoday.co.im/news/business/panama_s_the_place_to_be_1_1782652?action=logout |title=Panama's the Place to be |publisher=''[[Isle_of_Man_Examiner|Isle of Man Examiner]]'' |date=November 1, 2001 |accessdate=March 8, 2013 |archive-date=2013-04-13 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130413003816/http://www.iomtoday.co.im/news/business/panama_s_the_place_to_be_1_1782652?action=logout |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

=== 英属维尔京群岛 ===
莫萨克于1987年开始在[[英屬維爾京群島|英属维尔京群岛]]运营。自成立以来，事务所在该岛拥有超过10万家公司。<ref name=":0">{{cite web|url=https://panamapapers.icij.org/20160403-mossack-fonseca-offshore-secrets.html|title=Panamanian Law Firm Is Gatekeeper To Vast Flow of Murky Offshore Secrets|last=Hamilton|first=Martha|date=2016-04-03|publisher=International Consortium of Investigative Journalists|access-date=2016-04-04|archive-date=2016-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405080933/https://panamapapers.icij.org/20160403-mossack-fonseca-offshore-secrets.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 纽埃 ===
事务所与[[紐埃|纽埃]]国进行磋商，后者试图成为[[离岸金融中心|离岸金融中心]]，并通过他们的巴拿马总部为全国专门管理该业务<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZK6kAgAAQBAJ|title=Global Shell Games: Experiments in Transnational Relations, Crime, and Terrorism|last=Findley|first=Michael G.|last2=Nielson|first2=Daniel L.|last3=Sharman|first3=J. C.|date=2014-01-23|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=9781107729681|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pOdvLS954qsC|title=Tax Havens|last=Fossen|first=Anthony Van|date=2012-01-01|publisher={{link-en|University of Queensland Press|Univ. of Queensland Press|University of Queensland Press}}|isbn=9781921902239|language=en}}</ref>。不过，2001年美国银行开始禁止银行转账到纽埃，导致业务于2005年关闭<ref name=":0" />。事务所的客户帐户从纽埃转移到[[美屬薩摩亞|美属萨摩亚]]<ref name="VICE" />。

== 争议 ==
事务所涉嫌帮助外国公民逃避当地税法<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/rob-magazine/how-i-learned-to-avoid-the-taxman-in-the-british-virgin-islands/article567793/?page=all |title=How I learned to avoid the taxman in the British Virgin Islands |author=Trevor Cole |accessdate=March 8, 2013 |date=January 27, 2011 |publisher=''[[Globe_&_Mail|Globe & Mail]]''}}</ref><ref name="sd" /><ref name="VICE" />和[[国际制裁|国际制裁]]<ref name="VICE">{{cite web|last1=Silverstein|first1=Ken|title=The Law Firm That Works with Oligarchs, Money Launderers, and Dictators|url=http://www.vice.com/read/evil-llc-0000524-v21n12|website=Vice|publisher=Vice Media|date=3 December 2014|accessdate=16 December 2014|archive-date=2016-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404175141/https://www.vice.com/read/evil-llc-0000524-v21n12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Cox|first1=Simon|title=Panama Papers: Mossack Fonseca 'helped firms subject to sanctions'|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-35959604|website=BBC News|accessdate=5 April 2016|date=4 April 2016|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226142155/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-35959604|dead-url=no}}</ref>。事务所的创办人认为这只是帮助这些客户保护隐私，并且它现在符合“[[了解你的客户|了解你的客户]]”的规定<ref name=":1" />。

=== 阿根廷洗钱 ===
{{Main article|The Route of the K-Money|l1=K-资金路线}}

2014年，莫萨克·冯赛卡（MF）企业服务受到一个[[对冲基金|对冲基金]]的传唤，后者谋求收回阿根廷政府的资金。该基金称MF创造了空壳公司将来自政府的资金传递给[[克里斯蒂娜·费尔南德斯·德基什内尔|基什内尔]]家族的盟友{{Le|拉萨·罗贝兹|Lázaro Báez}}。<ref name=":0" /><ref name="VICE" />莫萨克·冯赛卡声称这不是MF企业服务的拥有者，但内华达州的法官裁定针对莫萨克·冯赛卡的传票是有效的<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.courthousenews.com/2015/03/18/judge-oks-hunt-for-argentine-millions.htm|title=Judge OKs hunt for Argentine millions|last=Heuer|first=Mike|date=2015-03-18|access-date=2016-04-04 |agency=[[Courthouse_News_Service|Courthouse News Service]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2014-08-13/paul-singer-gets-ok-to-chase-argentina-money-trail-to-nevada-1-|title=Singer Gets OK to Chase Argentina Money Trail to Nevada|last=Pearson|first=Sophia|date=2014-08-13|website=Bloomberg.com|access-date=2016-04-05}}</ref>。

=== 德国商业银行 ===
2015年2月，在德国政府对[[洗钱|洗钱]]和[[德国商业银行|德国商业银行]]的[[逃税|逃税]]计划的调查中，事务所牵涉其中。<ref name="sd">{{cite web|last1=Leyendecker|first1=Hans|title=Steueraffäre erschüttert Commerzbank|url=http://www.sueddeutsche.de/wirtschaft/luxemburg-steueraffaere-erschuettert-commerzbank-1.2366678|accessdate=26 February 2015|language=de}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://global.handelsblatt.com/edition/131/ressort/finance/article/in-panama-a-german-king-of-shelf-companies|title=In Panama, a German King of Shell Companies|last=Braecher|first=Michael|date=2015-03-09|website=Handelsblatt Global Edition|language=en-US|access-date=2016-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160407224404/https://global.handelsblatt.com/edition/131/ressort/finance/article/in-panama-a-german-king-of-shelf-companies|archive-date=2016-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 巴西石油 ===
{{Main article|{{link-en|洗车行动|Operation Car Wash}}}}2016年1月，事务所巴西办事处的员工被指控与当时的[[巴西石油|巴西石油公司]]腐败丑闻有关。在这种情况下，法官指控“莫萨克·冯赛卡为离岸团体的开办提供服务，至少四家代理商参与了洗钱计划”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.prensa.com/in_english/Mossack-Fonseca_21_4403019655.html|title=Mossack Fonseca employees face charges in Brazil|date=2016-01-28|website=[[La_Prensa_(Panama_City)|La Prensa]]|access-date=2016-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404153854/http://www.prensa.com/in_english/Mossack-Fonseca_21_4403019655.html|archive-date=2016-04-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。事务所回应道巴西办事处是“特许经营”，不受巴拿马的主办公室控制<ref name=":0" />。事务所创始人辞去巴拿马政府顾问一职以着眼于巴西的指控，并说事务所已经澄清<ref name=":1" />。

===“巴拿马文件”泄露===
{{Main|巴拿马文件}}
2016年4月3日，德国《[[南德意志报|南德意志报]]》报道事务所1150万份机密文档已被泄露给记者。这些文档被称为“巴拿马文件”，披露了客户如何将数十亿美元藏于[[避税港|避税港]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Harding|first1=Luke|title=Revealed: the $2bn offshore trail that leads to Vladimir Putin|url=http://www.theguardian.com/news/2016/apr/03/panama-papers-money-hidden-offshore|accessdate=3 April 2016|work=The Guardian|date=3 April 2016}}</ref>。其包含的文档可追溯到20世纪70年代，2.6[[太字节|太字节]]的文件由匿名人士在2015年提供给《南德意志报》，随后移交给总部设在华盛顿的[[国际调查记者同盟|国际调查记者同盟]]（ICIJ）<ref>{{cite news |title=Data trove offers glimpse of how the rich hide their money |url=http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2016/04/03/world/europe/ap-panama-papers.html?_r=0 |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |date=April 4, 2016 |accessdate=April 4, 2016 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Panama Papers: Mossack Fonseca leak reveals elite's tax havens |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-35918844 |last=Bilton |first=Richard |date=April 4, 2016 |website=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |accessdate=2016-04-07 |archive-date=2018-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180730052546/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-35918844 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Panama Papers|url=https://panamapapers.icij.org/|website=International Consortium of Investigative Journalists|accessdate=2016-04-07|archive-date=2018-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180210092113/https://panamapapers.icij.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

事务所表示这一报导“曲解”了他们的工作和他们提供给客户的服务<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mossfon.com/media/|title=Statement Regarding Recent Media Coverage|date=2016-04-04|website=Mossack Fonseca|access-date=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-04-05|archive-url=https://archive.today/20160405122919/http://www.mossfon.com/media/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他们已通知客户媒体获得的文件是侵入电子邮件服务器的黑客获取的<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.elespanol.com/espana/20160403/114488656_0.html|title=Los papeles de Panamá: Pilar de Borbón, Messi y Almodóvar, entre los investigados|last=Urreiztieta|first=Esteban|date=2016-04-03|publisher=El Español|access-date=2016-04-05}}</ref>。《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》认为该事务所的[[信息安全|信息安全]]较差，关键工具还在使用旧版本<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2016/04/05/panama-papers-amazon-encryption-epic-leak/#2043d26e1df5|title=From Encrypted Drives To Amazon's Cloud -- The Amazing Flight Of The Panama Papers|last=Fox-Brewster|first=Thomas|date=2016-04-05|website=Forbes|access-date=2016-04-05}}</ref>。

